content:
[[module css]]

.hfcontainer {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-image: url('http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Ahf-poster/Herman-Fuller-background.png');
    background-size: 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    color: #BEB192;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px #000;
}

.hfheader {
    padding: 0;
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 80px;
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
}

.hfnarrowcontent {
    width: 20%;
    font-size: 2em;
    font-family: eastmarketregular, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0% 2%;
    padding-bottom: 0px;
    margin: 0;
    vertical-align: top;
    display: inline-block;
}

.hfnarrowcontent p {
    line-height: 110%;
}

.hftitle {
   font-size: 3.2em;
   font-family: eastmarketregular, sans-serif;
   font-weight: bold;
   text-align: center;
   height: 75px;
   width: 100%;
   padding: 0;
   margin: 0;
   display: block;
}

.hfwidecontent {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    font-family: eastmarketregular, sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: -20px;
    margin: 0;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.hfwidecontent p {
    line-height: 120%;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0px 15px;
}

.hffooter {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    font-family: eastmarketregular, sans-serif;
    padding: 0px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8em;
}

.hfpic {
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    background-position: center center; 
    vertical-align: middle;
}

.hfpicframe {
    background-image: url('http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Ahf-poster/frame.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat; 
    background-position: center center; 
    background-size: contain;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: inline-block;
}

.hfpic-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    vertical-align: middle;
}

.table {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 1000px) {
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 18pt;
    }

    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.8em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 975px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 3.1em;
       height: 60px;
    }

    .hfpic {
        height: 95%;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 950px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.5em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 350px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        height: 100%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 15px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 890px) {
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 15pt;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 300px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 830px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.2em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 13pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 10px 0px;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 225px;
        vertical-align: top;
    }
    .hfpic {
        height: 95%;
        width: 40%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.7em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.8em;
       height: 65px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        font-size: 18pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 30px 0px;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 380px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        height: 85%;
        width: 40%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 715px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.5em;
       height: 50px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 22%;
        font-size: 17pt;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 340px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        height: 90%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 675px) {
    .hfpic {
        height: 80%;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 625px) {
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.3em;
       height: 40px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 20%;
        font-size: 15pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 20px 0px;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 325px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        width: 45%;
        height: 85%;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 585px) {
    .hfheader {
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 60px;
    }
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.1em;
       height: 25px;
    }
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 290px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        width: 45%;
        height: 80%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.8em;
    }
}

@media only screen and (max-width: 515px) {
    .hfpic-container {
        height: 260px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        width: 45%;
        height: 85%;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 19%;
        font-size: 12pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 12px 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent{
        margin-top: 0px;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.7em;
    }
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 460px) {
    .hfheader {
    padding-top: 20px;
    height: 40px;
    }
    .hftitle {
       font-size: 2.1em;
       height: 25px;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent {
        width: 19%;
        font-size: 10pt;
    }
    .hfnarrowcontent p{
        margin: 12px 0px;
    }
     .hfpic-container {
        height: 200px;
    }
    .hfpic {
        width: 45%;
        height: 85%;
    }
    .hfwidecontent p{
        font-size: 0.6em;
    }
}

[[/module]]

[[include credit:start]]
**タイトル:** ハーマンフラー主催：｢女の死｣と｢奇跡の誕生」
**著者:** ©︎[[*user indonootoko]]
**作成年:** 2018
[[include credit:end]]
@@ @@
[[div class="hfcontainer"]]
[[div class="table"]]
    [[div class="hfheader"]]
     @@ @@
    [[/div]]

    [[div class="hftitle"]]
     ｢女の死｣と｢奇跡の誕生｣
    [[/div]]

    [[div class="hfpic-container"]]

    [[div class="hfnarrowcontent"]]
     この女の死様を見に来るのだ！

　　
教師という夢と悪魔達に裏切られ！


壮絶なる悲哀に飲み込まれた！


　　
    [[/div]]

        [[div class="hfpic" style="background-image: url('http://scp-jp-sandbox3.wdfiles.com/local--files/draft%3Aindonootoko-1/tanaka1.png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; background-size: contain;"]]
            [[div class="hfpicframe"]]
            @@ @@
            [[/div]]
        [[/div]]

    [[div class="hfnarrowcontent"]]
     この悲歎は死ぬ程度では消えないのだ！


女の死後残される怨嗟が生む奇跡を見よ！


魂と思念が作り出す神秘を見に来るのだ！
    [[/div]]

    [[/div]]

    [[div class="hfwidecontent"]]
     極東の地で教師をする女//Toshiko Tanaka。// 女は夢を叶えたが夢は絶望へと変わり、悪魔たちは女を銷魂の淵へ叩き落した。女はショーの日に自ら命を絶つ！しかし女の持つ壮絶な絶念は死如きでは清算できない。この不幸な女の死様を見に来い、そして世にも珍しい"イリュージョン"誕生の瞬間を見逃すな！
    [[/div]]

    [[div class="hffooter"]]
     一夜限り

1月21日深夜0時、日本国██県██市 特設サーカス場にて。
 見られるのはこれっきりだよ！ 寄ってらっしゃい、見てらっしゃい！
    [[/div]]

 [[/div]]
[[/div]]
　
　
　
